           SHORT="Versatile replacement for vmstat, iostat and ifstat"
cat << EOF
Dstat is a versatile replacement for vmstat, iostat, and ifstat.
It overcomes some of the limitations of these tools and adds some
extra features. It allows you to view all of your system resources
instantly; you can, for example, compare disk usage in combination
with interrupts from your IDE controller, or compare the network 
bandwidth numbers directly with the disk throughput (in the same
interval).
EOF
